<file xmlns:its="http://www.w3.org/2005/11/its" xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:qh5="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiv2p2_html5_v1p0" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <sharedstimuli>
        <sharedstimulus id="assets/d67a0fbc6355edc102f28/passage NEW.xml">
            <label key="e1b62ec8dd135e40e3a0842b3ea645f7">
                <text>Efficacy of Face Masks</text>
            </label>
            <label key="44f12dbf10c5b3b7e01d5a219bda4b24">
                <text>This graph is from a scientific article and was carefully checked for accuracy and validity. It shows how the spread of a respiratory virus, such as influenza, can be affected by:</text>
            </label>
            <label key="1e7bfd7d777af2eb129c87cddbec065e">
                <text>the percentage of the public who wear masks (adherence)</text>
            </label>
            <label key="cec19722984b7472cea77423063a710f">
                <text>how well masks block the virus (efficacy).</text>
            </label>
            <label key="729676344f049f44e93b9ec5bcb7dd5e">
                <text>
                    <strong>The resulting reproduction number, <em>R</em><sub>e</sub>, is the average number of people who will contract a contagious disease from one person with that disease.</strong>
                </text>
            </label>
            <label key="04284a15a43f01b851069904f354c767">
                <text>The spread of a respiratory virus eventually stops if the value of <em>R</em><sub>e</sub> is less than 1. That means, on average, each infected person infects less than one other person.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="74be375aa04773ba8517c6801c333504">
                <text>More people wear masks</text>
            </label>
            <label key="59ecd7e9e7848fa0440cbdb5180b2168">
                <text><strong>Adherence:</strong><br/>Percentage of the public who wears masks</text>
            </label>
            <label key="27224bdd467832062cb4e600aebf6168">
                <text>Fewer people wear masks</text>
            </label>
            <label key="5e3cdf452375612e55f27b67f59cd4bb">
                <text>Mask blocks less virus particles</text>
            </label>
            <label key="feaa6b99ccc0a2f2ad7f8d05447ea40b">
                <text><strong>Efficacy:</strong><br/>How well the mask blocks the virus</text>
            </label>
            <label key="dfcc52273a2d6641f4d3226e6319cff2">
                <text>Mask blocks more virus particles</text>
            </label>
            <label key="c1e44a0fbc607884bd16cb7f924b22e8">
                <text>
                    <strong>Rₑ = 1 </strong>
                </text>
            </label>
            <label key="80227d9d196a2cd29ae0f6456d1a7a75">
                <text>Rₑ = 1.5</text>
            </label>
            <label key="fb04f3ad45abd1947bd07445ca6b2ff6">
                <text>Rₑ = 2</text>
            </label>
        </sharedstimulus>
    </sharedstimuli>
