        <item id="i6355efc920a161990cf3d099dddcc6ab5">
            <label key="10f851b884d95df352597530e3ffb96c">
                <text>Consider the situation where there is a shortage of high-quality face masks (90–100% efficacy).<div></div><div><span>According to the data presented on the right, would lower quality masks (60% efficacy) contain the disease?</span></div></text>
            </label>
            <label key="146acc4e1d0cb6ef3b8172f382df6421">
                <text>Yes, under the condition that at least 80% of the population will use them.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="eb63e6f5726f4e3eb728b90954e4232e">
                <text>Yes, because an efficacy of 60% means that <em>R</em><sub>e</sub> is less than 1.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="354bf408ac6baaeaa4a51d7f6229d031">
                <text>No, because these masks block only half of the virus particles.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="84608f09e36d7d40ce90919d286f5d84">
                <text>No, because not enough people would wear them.</text>
            </label>
        </item>
        <item id="i6355f2e52b071176312e9cb62ce6c96e89">
            <label key="507ae2da86c513956d71d6d4155512aa">
                <text>In one country, authorities encouraged the use of masks by distributing free FFP2 masks. These masks have an efficacy of 95%.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="2e24933ad4adcff683608b45e947aebb">
                <text>This intervention resulted in 45% of the population wearing FFP2 masks during a respiratory virus outbreak.</text>
            </label>
            <label key="a4732721abb01a18fb081354ef20f9bd">
                <text>Based on the data in the graph on the right, would this intervention be enough to stop the spread of the respiratory virus?</text>
            </label>
            <label key="a6105c0a611b41b08f1209506350279e">
                <text>yes</text>
            </label>
            <label key="7fa3b767c460b54a2be4d49030b349c7">
                <text>no</text>
            </label>
            <label key="de03d051471bf1872104f26fc81d6982">
                <text>Give a reason for your answer.</text>
            </label>
        </item>
